author: aonyx123
title: Great Bonus Item
review:
Box/Instructions

Comes in a Polybag with the purchase of the Lego Jurassic World video game at Target. No instructions.

Parts

5 individual parts. Amber piece printing looks great.

Minifigures

Dr. Wu has a double sided printed torso. Has printing on legs to extend lab coat. Double sided face with a happy face on one side and a smirking face on the other side.

The build

Unfortunately, this minifigure came pre-built. However, with the total amount of pieces in the set, it is understandable.

The completed model

N/A

Overall opinion

Great supplement to the Jurassic World sets. For $30, it is a great way to get the minifigure instead of buying the large set.
